Tawuni ya Cape Town inamangidwa ndi kampani ya Dutch East India Company (VOC) ngati malo operekera zofunika ku mabwato amene amapita kuzambwe kwa Africa komanso India. [[:en:Jan_van_Riebeeck|Jan Van  Riebeeck]] wa kampani ya VOC anafika pa 6 apulo mu chaka cha 1652 ndipo anakhazikitsa malo oyamba okhalapo azungu mu South Africa. Kenaka tawuniyi inakhula kwambiri kuposa cholinga chomwe inayikhazikilitsila ndipo inakhalamalo a zachuma komanso chikhalidwe kwa anthu ochoka ku ulaya.

Anthu oyamilila kukhala mudelali amakha ku maphanga a Peers ku fish Hoel muzaka zoposela 15, 000 kapena 12, 000 zapitazo. Padakali pano anthu amangodziwa zinthu zochepa za anthu amenewa chifukwa umboni woyamba wolembedwa umapezeka pa zomwe Bartolomeu Dias ananena mu chaka cha 1488. Iyeyu anali mzungu woyamba kufika kumalowa ndipo anatchula malowa "Cape of Storms" (''Cabo das Tormentas'').  KOma malowa anatchulidwa dzina lina ndi John II of Portugal as "Cape of Good Hope" (''Cabo da Boa Esperança'') chifukwa cha chiyembekezo chimene chinalipo chopeza njira ya panyanja kukafika ku India. Vasco da gama analemba zowona malowa mu chaka cha 1497. Muchaka cha 1510, pankhondo ya Salt river,  Francisco de Almeida ndi ankhondo ake anagonjetsedwa ndi Goringhaiqua, gulu lina la chikhoekhoe. Muzaka za ma 16  chakuti,  mabwato azungu amayima pa gombe la Table bay kupita ku India. Amachita malona a fodya, kopa, ayiloni ndi anthu achikhoekhoe, kusinthana ndi nyama ndi zinthu zina.

